<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>意见：</strong></p>
</div>
<div class="blockquote">
<p><span style="color: black"><strong>O5-<span class="no">1</span>：</strong>在<span class="no">我目</span>睹<span class="no">人</span>类与<span class="no">黑</span>暗抗<span class="no">争</span>的千古岁<span class="no">月</span>之中，<span class="no">我从</span>未见过<span class="no">如</span>今天般黯<span class="no">淡</span>的<span class="no">一</span>天。<span class="no">这</span>将是秩序之<span class="no">死</span>亡。<span class="no">这</span>将是光明之<span class="no">死</span>亡。</span></p>
</div>
<br />
<span style="font-size:50%;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></span></div>
