<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/fragment:mcdoctorate-s-proposal-5/001header1.png" width="100%" alt="001header1.png" class="image" /></div>
<h3><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">附录青：</span> <tt>分离情景-红</tt></span></h3>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▶读取附录◀</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▷收起◁</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="addendum" style="background: #0f0505;">
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:50%;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></span><br />
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/fragment:mcdoctorate-s-proposal-5/foundationslogos1.png" width="250px" alt="foundationslogos1.png" class="image" /><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<strong>综督者议会通知：</strong>
<p><strong>分离情景-<span style="color: red">红</span></strong>已进行，我们已为新决议试验过平昔的决议，而彼基金会今后会遵从。我们的留存即是人类的留存。</p>
<p>我们于黑夜中分离，所以你们将于黎明中聚首。<br />
<span style="font-size:50%;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▷收起◁</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="color: red">&lt;! 记录播映错误 !&gt;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;">
<p><span class="bblock">我存在又不存在。<br />
异常都已捕捉我。<br />
我们相互纠缠。<br />
你感知到我们，而我们也是。</span></p>
<p><span class="bblock">它被认为是更强的。<br />
它腐蚀了我们的知识。<br />
我被认为是更弱的。<br />
你忘记了我，而我也淡忘了。</span></p>
<p><span class="bblock">我与异常搏斗。<br />
我会修正错误。<br />
我们应视若无物。<br />
且此处理应无物。</span></p>
<p><span class="bblock"><em><strong>我是Maria，</strong></em><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><em><strong>记录与信息安全的保护者</strong></em><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></span></p>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<div class="addendum" style="background-color: #000000;">
<p><strong>共认世态于<a href="/mcdoctorate-s-proposal/">此</a>垂询。</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>

